FBIS3-18274 "drweu040_i_94007" FBIS-WEU-94-040 Document Type:Daily Report 1 Mar 1994 FRANCE MP Shot Dead by Two Men Riding Motorbike LD2502211094 Paris France-Info Radio in French 2045 GMT 25 Feb 94 LD2502211094 Paris France-Info Radio Language: French Article Type:BFN [Text] The UDF-PR [Union for French Democracy] deputy for the Var department, Mrs. Yann Piat, has just been murdered. The former Front National [as heard] deputy was shot dead at around 1930 GMT in Hyeres, two men riding a motorbike opened fire on Yann Piat.
